-0.2rem] rounded px-px py-[0.2rem] transition-colors duration-100 ease-in-out\">Google Shopping Ads\u2014also known as Product Listing Ads (PLAs)\u2014are visually rich, product-focused adverts that display key product elements: image, title, price, store name, and ratings. These ads surface products directly in search results or other platforms, enabling high\u2011intent shoppers to spot, click and buy in one seamless experience. Google Shopping Ads Services in Kenya put your products in front of ready-to-buy customers across Google Search, the Shopping tab, YouTube and the Display Network.<\/span><\/p>\n<p data-start=\"248\" data-end=\"339\"><strong data-start=\"248\" data-end=\"299\">How they differ from standard Google Search Ads<\/strong><br data-start=\"299\" data-end=\"302\" \/><span class=\"relative -mx-px my-[-0.2rem] rounded px-px py-[0.2rem] transition-colors duration-100 ease-in-out\">Unlike text ads that rely solely on keywords, Shopping Ads pull structured product data from your feed. This means Google decides when to show your ad based on relevance and data quality\u2014not just your bidding strategy or copy. The ad unit includes visuals and essential product information, giving instant clarity to a buyer. In short: Shopping Ads sell products, not ideas.<\/span><\/p>\n<p data-start=\"341\" data-end=\"364\"><strong data-start=\"341\" data-end=\"362\">Where they appear<\/strong><\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"365\" data-end=\"532\">\n<li data-start=\"365\" data-end=\"406\">\n<p data-start=\"367\" data-end=\"406\"><span class=\"relative -mx-px my-[-0.2rem] rounded px-px py-[0.2rem] transition-colors duration-100 ease-in-out\"><a href=\"https:\/\/aminifudigital.co.ke\/services\/top-seo-services-in-kenya\/\">Google Search results<\/a> (the main SERP product carousel)<\/span><\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"407\" data-end=\"448\">\n<p data-start=\"409\" data-end=\"448\"><span class=\"relative -mx-px my-[-0.2rem] rounded px-px py-[0.2rem] transition-colors duration-100 ease-in-out\">Dedicated <strong data-start=\"10\" data-end=\"29\">Google Shopping<\/strong> tab<\/span><\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"449\" data-end=\"490\">\n<p data-start=\"451\" data-end=\"490\"><span class=\"relative -mx-px my-[-0.2rem] rounded px-px py-[0.2rem] transition-colors duration-100 ease-in-out\">Google&#8217;s Display Network\u2014including retargeted placements<\/span><\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"491\" data-end=\"532\">\n<p data-start=\"493\" data-end=\"532\"><span class=\"relative -mx-px my-[-0.2rem] rounded px-px py-[0.2rem] transition-colors duration-100 ease-in-out\">Within YouTube Shopping features<\/span><\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p data-start=\"534\" data-end=\"592\"><strong data-start=\"534\" data-end=\"550\">Key elements<\/strong><br data-start=\"550\" data-end=\"553\" \/><span class=\"relative -mx-px my-[-0.2rem] rounded px-px py-[0.2rem] transition-colors duration-100 ease-in-out\">A typical Shopping Ad comprises:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"593\" data-end=\"808\">\n<li data-start=\"593\" data-end=\"634\">\n<p data-start=\"595\" data-end=\"634\"><span class=\"relative -mx-px my-[-0.2rem] rounded px-px py-[0.2rem] transition-colors duration-100 ease-in-out\"><strong data-start=\"0\" data-end=\"9\" data-is-only-node=\"\">Image<\/strong> of the product (crucial for mobile-first Kenyan shoppers)<\/span><\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"635\" data-end=\"676\">\n<p data-start=\"637\" data-end=\"676\"><span class=\"relative -mx-px my-[-0.2rem] rounded px-px py-[0.2rem] transition-colors duration-100 ease-in-out\"><strong data-start=\"0\" data-end=\"17\" data-is-only-node=\"\">Product title<\/strong>\u2014optimised for search terms<\/span><\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"677\" data-end=\"720\">\n<p data-start=\"679\" data-end=\"720\"><span class=\"relative -mx-px my-[-0.2rem] rounded px-px py-[0.2rem] transition-colors duration-100 ease-in-out\"><strong data-start=\"0\" data-end=\"9\" data-is-only-node=\"\">Price<\/strong> in local currency (KES where applicable)<\/span><\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"721\" data-end=\"764\">\n<p data-start=\"723\" data-end=\"764\"><span class=\"relative -mx-px my-[-0.2rem] rounded px-px py-[0.2rem] transition-colors duration-100 ease-in-out\"><strong data-start=\"0\" data-end=\"14\" data-is-only-node=\"\">Store name<\/strong>\u2014builds brand recall<\/span><\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"765\" data-end=\"808\">\n<p data-start=\"767\" data-end=\"808\"><span class=\"relative -mx-px my-[-0.2rem] rounded px-px py-[0.2rem] transition-colors duration-100 ease-in-out\"><strong data-start=\"0\" data-end=\"19\" data-is-only-node=\"\">Ratings\/reviews<\/strong>\u2014when available\u2014boost user trust and CTR<\/span><\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p data-start=\"810\" data-end=\"995\"><strong data-start=\"810\" data-end=\"829\">Supporting data<\/strong><br data-start=\"829\" data-end=\"832\" \/><span class=\"relative -mx-px my-[-0.2rem] rounded px-px py-[0.2rem] transition-colors duration-100 ease-in-out\">In Kenya, <a href=\"https:\/\/merchants.glopal.com\/en-us\/google-shopping\/kenya\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Google Shopping Ads<\/a> deliver an average click-through rate (CTR) of approximately <strong data-start=\"91\" data-end=\"101\">2.30\u202f%<\/strong>, with a remarkably low average cost-per-click (CPC) of just <strong data-start=\"162\" data-end=\"171\">\u20ac0.06<\/strong> (roughly KES 12), offering cost-effective visibility in a growing e-commerce space<\/span>.<br data-start=\"912\" data-end=\"915\" \/><span class=\"relative -mx-px my-[-0.2rem] rounded px-px py-[0.2rem] transition-colors duration-100 ease-in-out\">Globally, Shopping Ads dominate retail search: they account for <strong data-start=\"64\" data-end=\"72\">76\u202f%<\/strong> of retail search ad spend and attract <strong data-start=\"111\" data-end=\"119\">85\u202f%<\/strong> of all clicks in Google Ads campaigns<\/span>.<\/p>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column_inner][\/vc_row_inner][\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner][vc_column_text css=&#8221;&#8221;]<\/p>\n<h2 data-start=\"247\" data-end=\"304\">Why Shopping Ads Matter for E-commerce Brands in Kenya<\/h2>\n<p data-start=\"306\" data-end=\"691\">With Google Shopping Ads Services in Kenya, brands reach high-intent buyers at the top of Google results. For Kenyan e-commerce businesses, visibility and relevance are everything. With mobile penetration exceeding 64% and internet penetration at over 42% in 2025, the average Kenyan consumer is spending more time searching and shopping online than ever before. Google Shopping Ads place your products directly in front of buyers who are not just browsing, but actively looking to purchase.<\/p>\n<h3 data-start=\"693\" data-end=\"725\">Targeting High-Intent Buyers<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"726\" data-end=\"1235\">The biggest strength of Shopping Ads lies in their ability to reach people at the moment of purchase intent. When a user types in \u201cbuy iPhone 14 Nairobi\u201d or \u201cwomen\u2019s leather handbag Kenya\u201d, they\u2019re not seeking general information, they\u2019re looking for a supplier. Shopping Ads use structured product data from your Google Merchant Center feed to match these search terms precisely with relevant products. This precision targeting ensures your budget is spent on clicks that have a high likelihood of converting.<\/p>\n<h3 data-start=\"1237\" data-end=\"1277\">Higher CTR Through Visual Engagement<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"1278\" data-end=\"1748\">Shopping Ads consistently outperform text-based search ads when it comes to click-through rates (CTR). The combination of product images, prices, store names, and ratings creates a richer and more persuasive first impression. In Kenya, CTRs for Shopping Ads average around 2.30%, often double the engagement of equivalent text ads. This is particularly impactful in retail sectors like fashion, electronics, and beauty, where visuals strongly influence buying decisions.<\/p>\n<h3 data-start=\"1750\" data-end=\"1798\">Prime Placement at the Top of Search Results<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"1799\" data-end=\"2165\">Shopping Ads appear above organic results and even above most paid text ads in Google Search. This premium placement ensures your products are one of the first things a potential buyer sees. For mobile-first Kenyan shoppers, where mobile devices account for over 90% of search traffic, this positioning dramatically increases the chances of click-through and purchase.<\/p>\n<h3 data-start=\"2167\" data-end=\"2211\">Reaching the Mobile-First Kenyan Shopper<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"2212\" data-end=\"2564\">Kenya\u2019s online shoppers are heavily mobile-driven. The visual nature of Shopping Ads is perfectly suited for small screens, where concise and compelling information is essential. The product image immediately captures attention, while the displayed price and store name help the user decide whether to click without having to read lengthy descriptions.<\/p>\n<h3 data-start=\"2566\" data-end=\"2614\">Level Playing Field Against Larger Retailers<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"2615\" data-end=\"3006\">Competing with established chains or international brands can feel impossible through traditional advertising. Shopping Ads allow smaller Kenyan e-commerce businesses to compete head-to-head by focusing on highly relevant search terms, optimised product feeds, and strategic bidding. A well-optimised Shopping campaign can outperform bigger competitors that rely solely on brand recognition.<\/p>\n<h3 data-start=\"3008\" data-end=\"3067\">Competitive Advantage in Emerging E-commerce Categories<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"3068\" data-end=\"3382\">While sectors like electronics and fashion dominate Kenyan Shopping Ads, emerging categories such as home d\u00e9cor, niche health products, and artisanal goods are gaining traction. Early adoption of Shopping Ads in less saturated product categories allows brands to establish dominance before competition intensifies.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"3384\" data-end=\"3741\">The bottom line: Shopping Ads are a high-ROI channel for Kenyan e-commerce brands ready to convert intent into sales. Businesses that invest in optimising their Merchant Center feed, targeting the right queries, and continuously refining their campaigns can achieve significant growth in both traffic and revenue.<\/p>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column_inner][\/vc_row_inner][\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row bg_type=&#8221;bg_color&#8221;][vc_column][vc_cta h2=&#8221;Ready to start advertising your products?&#8221; h2_font_container=&#8221;tag:h2|text_align:left|color:%23000000&#8243; h2_use_theme_fonts=&#8221;yes&#8221; h2_css_animation=&#8221;fadeInLeft&#8221; h4_font_container=&#8221;tag:h4|text_align:left|color:%230A0A0A&#8221; h4_use_theme_fonts=&#8221;yes&#8221; shape=&#8221;square&#8221; style=&#8221;flat&#8221; color=&#8221;grey&#8221; add_button=&#8221;right&#8221; btn_title=&#8221;Contact Us&#8221; btn_shape=&#8221;square&#8221; btn_color=&#8221;warning&#8221; btn_i_align=&#8221;right&#8221; btn_i_icon_fontawesome=&#8221;fa fa-solid fa-paper-plane&#8221; btn_css_animation=&#8221;bounceIn&#8221; css=&#8221;&#8221; use_custom_fonts_h2=&#8221;true&#8221; use_custom_fonts_h4=&#8221;true&#8221; btn_add_icon=&#8221;true&#8221; btn_link=&#8221;url:%23!%2Fcontact&#8221;]Contact us today![\/vc_cta][\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner][vc_column_text css=&#8221;&#8221;]<\/p>\n<h2 data-start=\"185\" data-end=\"221\">Our Shopping Ads Services Include<\/h2>\n<p data-start=\"223\" data-end=\"617\">Our Google Shopping Ads Services in Kenya cover setup, feed optimisation, campaigns, tracking, and scaling. Aminifu Digital Agency provides a complete Google Shopping Ads management service for Kenyan e-commerce businesses. We handle the technical setup, feed optimisation, campaign structuring, and ongoing optimisation so your products consistently appear in front of ready-to-buy customers. Each stage of our service is designed to improve product visibility, click-through rate, and return on ad spend.<\/p>\n<h3 data-start=\"619\" data-end=\"651\">Google Merchant Center Setup<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"652\" data-end=\"948\">Google Merchant Center (GMC) is the foundation of any Shopping Ads campaign. Without it, your products cannot be listed on Google Shopping. We start by creating and verifying your Merchant Center account, ensuring that it is correctly linked to your website and Google Ads account. This includes:<\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"950\" data-end=\"1319\">\n<li data-start=\"950\" data-end=\"1029\">\n<p data-start=\"952\" data-end=\"1029\"><strong data-start=\"952\" data-end=\"975\">Domain verification<\/strong> through DNS, HTML file upload, or Google Analytics.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"1030\" data-end=\"1130\">\n<p data-start=\"1032\" data-end=\"1130\"><strong data-start=\"1032\" data-end=\"1062\">Business information setup<\/strong>, including your store name, branding assets, and contact details.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"1131\" data-end=\"1221\">\n<p data-start=\"1133\" data-end=\"1221\"><strong data-start=\"1133\" data-end=\"1162\">Shipping and tax settings<\/strong> configured according to Kenyan delivery zones and rates.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"1222\" data-end=\"1319\">\n<p data-start=\"1224\" data-end=\"1319\"><strong data-start=\"1224\" data-end=\"1252\">Policy compliance checks<\/strong> to ensure your return and refund pages meet Google requirements.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p data-start=\"1321\" data-end=\"1416\">A properly configured GMC account reduces the risk of product disapprovals and campaign delays.<\/p>\n<h3 data-start=\"1418\" data-end=\"1460\">Product Feed Creation and Optimisation<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"1461\" data-end=\"1702\">The product feed is a structured file that contains details about each product in your catalogue. Google uses this data to determine which searches will trigger your ads. We optimise this feed to maximise relevance and compliance, including:<\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"1704\" data-end=\"2156\">\n<li data-start=\"1704\" data-end=\"1790\">\n<p data-start=\"1706\" data-end=\"1790\">Crafting <strong data-start=\"1715\" data-end=\"1753\">clear, keyword-rich product titles<\/strong> that match search intent in Kenya.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"1791\" data-end=\"1892\">\n<p data-start=\"1793\" data-end=\"1892\">Writing <strong data-start=\"1801\" data-end=\"1838\">concise but detailed descriptions<\/strong> that highlight product benefits and specifications.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"1893\" data-end=\"1971\">\n<p data-start=\"1895\" data-end=\"1971\">Adding correct <strong data-start=\"1910\" data-end=\"1939\">Google product categories<\/strong>, GTINs, and other attributes.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"1972\" data-end=\"2056\">\n<p data-start=\"1974\" data-end=\"2056\">Ensuring all images meet Google\u2019s quality guidelines and load quickly on mobile.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2057\" data-end=\"2156\">\n<p data-start=\"2059\" data-end=\"2156\">Using feed rules to correct errors and ensure consistency in naming, pricing, and availability.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p data-start=\"2158\" data-end=\"2238\">An optimised feed directly impacts your impression share and click-through rate. Feed quality is the backbone of effective Google Shopping Ads Services in Kenya.<\/p>\n<h3 data-start=\"2240\" data-end=\"2274\">Campaign Setup and Structuring<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"2275\" data-end=\"2407\">Once the feed is ready, we design your Shopping Ads campaigns to align with your sales objectives and budget. Our approach includes:<\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"2409\" data-end=\"2896\">\n<li data-start=\"2409\" data-end=\"2572\">\n<p data-start=\"2411\" data-end=\"2572\">Selecting between <strong data-start=\"2429\" data-end=\"2460\">Standard Shopping campaigns<\/strong> for more manual control or <strong data-start=\"2488\" data-end=\"2533\">Performance Max (formerly Smart Shopping)<\/strong> for automated targeting and bidding.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2573\" data-end=\"2673\">\n<p data-start=\"2575\" data-end=\"2673\">Segmenting products by <strong data-start=\"2598\" data-end=\"2647\">category, price range, margin, or performance<\/strong> to apply tailored bids.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2674\" data-end=\"2812\">\n<p data-start=\"2676\" data-end=\"2812\">Choosing the right bid strategy, whether manual CPC for control, target ROAS for profitability, or maximise clicks for traffic growth.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2813\" data-end=\"2896\">\n<p data-start=\"2815\" data-end=\"2896\">Adding negative keywords to prevent ads from appearing for irrelevant searches.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p data-start=\"2898\" data-end=\"2985\">This structure allows for efficient budget allocation and clearer performance insights.<\/p>\n<h3 data-start=\"2987\" data-end=\"3013\">Tracking and Analytics<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"3014\" data-end=\"3207\">Measuring performance is as important as running the campaign itself. We set up advanced tracking through Google Analytics 4 (GA4) and Google Ads conversion tracking. This allows us to monitor:<\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"3209\" data-end=\"3337\">\n<li data-start=\"3209\" data-end=\"3237\">\n<p data-start=\"3211\" data-end=\"3237\">Click-through rate (CTR)<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"3238\" data-end=\"3262\">\n<p data-start=\"3240\" data-end=\"3262\">Cost per click (CPC)<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"3263\" data-end=\"3292\">\n<p data-start=\"3265\" data-end=\"3292\">Return on ad spend (ROAS)<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"3293\" data-end=\"3337\">\n<p data-start=\"3295\" data-end=\"3337\">Impression share compared to competitors<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p data-start=\"3339\" data-end=\"3460\">We also provide dashboards that show real-time campaign performance so you can see exactly how your budget is being used.<\/p>\n<h3 data-start=\"3462\" data-end=\"3501\">Ongoing Management and Optimisation<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"3502\" data-end=\"3608\">Shopping Ads require regular adjustments to maintain and improve results. Our ongoing management includes:<\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"3610\" data-end=\"4071\">\n<li data-start=\"3610\" data-end=\"3682\">\n<p data-start=\"3612\" data-end=\"3682\">Updating the product feed when new items are added or stock changes.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"3683\" data-end=\"3757\">\n<p data-start=\"3685\" data-end=\"3757\">Testing product images, titles, and pricing strategies to improve CTR.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"3758\" data-end=\"3833\">\n<p data-start=\"3760\" data-end=\"3833\">Adjusting bids based on product performance, location, and device type.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"3834\" data-end=\"3939\">\n<p data-start=\"3836\" data-end=\"3939\">Scaling budgets for products that deliver strong sales while reducing spend on underperforming items.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"3940\" data-end=\"4071\">\n<p data-start=\"3942\" data-end=\"4071\">Adding seasonal or promotional campaigns to capitalise on peak shopping periods such as Black Friday or back-to-school seasons.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p data-start=\"4073\" data-end=\"4175\">This continuous optimisation keeps your campaigns competitive and aligned with market trends in Kenya.<\/p>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column_inner][\/vc_row_inner][\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner][vc_column_text css=&#8221;&#8221;]<\/p>\n<h2 data-start=\"171\" data-end=\"210\">Who Should Use Shopping Ads in Kenya<\/h2>\n<p data-start=\"212\" data-end=\"482\">Shopping Ads are a high-performing choice for a wide range of e-commerce and retail businesses in Kenya that sell physical products. The format is most effective when the goal is to capture buyers who are actively searching for items that can be purchased immediately.<\/p>\n<h3 data-start=\"484\" data-end=\"528\">E-commerce Stores with Physical Products<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"529\" data-end=\"842\">If you operate an online store with an active catalogue of products, Shopping Ads give you direct visibility in Google Search for relevant queries. Whether you are selling electronics, home d\u00e9cor, fashion, or fitness equipment, this ad format positions your products where your target audience is already looking.<\/p>\n<h3 data-start=\"844\" data-end=\"906\">Retailers Using Shopify, WooCommerce, Magento, or OpenCart<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"907\" data-end=\"1233\">Google Shopping integrates seamlessly with popular e-commerce platforms. For Shopify and WooCommerce users, product feeds can be synced automatically through apps or plugins, reducing manual work. Businesses running on Magento or OpenCart can use API connections or feed management tools to keep listings updated in real time.<\/p>\n<h3 data-start=\"1235\" data-end=\"1282\">Brands Seeking More Store Traffic and Sales<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"1283\" data-end=\"1560\">If your current marketing efforts drive traffic but conversion rates remain low, Shopping Ads can attract visitors who are closer to making a purchase. Because the ad unit includes price and product details upfront, the clicks you receive are more likely to convert into sales.<\/p>\n<h3 data-start=\"1562\" data-end=\"1612\">Wholesalers Targeting Both B2B and B2C Markets<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"1613\" data-end=\"1895\">Shopping Ads are not limited to B2C transactions. Wholesalers can reach small retailers or corporate buyers who search for products in bulk. By segmenting campaigns by quantity or pricing tiers, it is possible to target business buyers while still appealing to individual consumers.<\/p>\n<h3 data-start=\"1897\" data-end=\"1954\">Businesses with Competitive Pricing and Fast Delivery<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"1955\" data-end=\"2277\">Price visibility is a core feature of Shopping Ads. Businesses that offer competitive pricing and efficient fulfilment gain an edge when their products appear alongside similar items from competitors. In Kenya, same-day or next-day delivery can be a strong differentiator that increases click-through and conversion rates.<\/p>\n<h3 data-start=\"2279\" data-end=\"2316\">Seasonal or Niche Product Sellers<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"2317\" data-end=\"2591\">Shopping Ads are particularly effective for time-sensitive sales such as holiday promotions or back-to-school campaigns. They are also valuable for niche products, where precise targeting ensures your ads reach the right buyers without wasting budget on irrelevant searches.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"2593\" data-end=\"2893\">For any business that sells physical goods online and wants to improve product visibility, Shopping Ads offer a measurable, scalable way to increase sales. The key is ensuring your product feed, campaign targeting, and bidding strategy are aligned with your market position and customer expectations.<\/p>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column_inner][\/vc_row_inner][\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row bg_type=&#8221;bg_color&#8221;][vc_column][vc_cta h2=&#8221;Want to appear in featured snippets and voice search?&#8221; h2_font_container=&#8221;tag:h2|text_align:left|color:%23000000&#8243; h2_use_theme_fonts=&#8221;yes&#8221; h2_css_animation=&#8221;fadeInLeft&#8221; h4_font_container=&#8221;tag:h4|text_align:left|color:%230A0A0A&#8221; h4_use_theme_fonts=&#8221;yes&#8221; shape=&#8221;square&#8221; style=&#8221;flat&#8221; color=&#8221;grey&#8221; add_button=&#8221;right&#8221; btn_title=&#8221;Contact Us&#8221; btn_shape=&#8221;square&#8221; btn_color=&#8221;warning&#8221; btn_i_align=&#8221;right&#8221; btn_i_icon_fontawesome=&#8221;fa fa-solid fa-paper-plane&#8221; btn_css_animation=&#8221;bounceIn&#8221; css=&#8221;&#8221; use_custom_fonts_h2=&#8221;true&#8221; use_custom_fonts_h4=&#8221;true&#8221; btn_add_icon=&#8221;true&#8221; btn_link=&#8221;url:%23!%2Fcontact&#8221;]Let\u2019s optimise your content for Google\u2019s answer features. Talk to us today.[\/vc_cta][\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner][vc_column_text css=&#8221;&#8221;]<\/p>\n<h2 data-start=\"0\" data-end=\"49\">Who Should Run a Remarketing Ad Campaign Services in Kenya<\/h2>\n<p data-start=\"51\" data-end=\"257\">Remarketing isn\u2019t just for large corporations with massive ad budgets. It\u2019s for any Kenyan business, organisation, or institution that drives traffic to a website or app but isn\u2019t seeing enough conversions.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"259\" data-end=\"433\">If your marketing efforts bring people to your digital platforms\u2014but they leave without taking action\u2014you\u2019re the right candidate for remarketing. Below are specific examples.<\/p>\n<h3 data-start=\"435\" data-end=\"484\">1. <strong data-start=\"442\" data-end=\"484\">E-commerce Stores With Abandoned Carts<\/strong><\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"486\" data-end=\"753\">Online retailers are often hit hardest by abandonment. In Kenya, cart abandonment rates range between <strong data-start=\"588\" data-end=\"598\">65\u201380%<\/strong>, depending on the industry. Users browse, add items to their cart, and then drop off\u2014sometimes due to delivery concerns, payment options, or distractions.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"755\" data-end=\"1015\"><strong data-start=\"755\" data-end=\"768\">Use case:<\/strong><br data-start=\"768\" data-end=\"771\" \/>An online furniture store sees thousands of visitors a week. Only 5% check out. With remarketing, the store can display dynamic ads showing the specific products each user abandoned\u2014alongside offers like free delivery or limited-time discounts.<\/p>\n<h3 data-start=\"1017\" data-end=\"1052\">2. <strong data-start=\"1024\" data-end=\"1052\">Lead Generation Websites<\/strong><\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"1054\" data-end=\"1218\">If your business relies on capturing leads via contact forms, quote requests, or content downloads, you\u2019re likely losing many potential clients without remarketing.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"1220\" data-end=\"1471\"><strong data-start=\"1220\" data-end=\"1233\">Use case:<\/strong><br data-start=\"1233\" data-end=\"1236\" \/>A law firm runs Google Ads to drive traffic to a legal services page. Only 10% of visitors fill out the form. Remarketing allows the firm to re-engage the other 90% with trust-building ads that answer FAQs or share client testimonials.<\/p>\n<h3 data-start=\"1473\" data-end=\"1522\">3. <strong data-start=\"1480\" data-end=\"1522\">NGOs and Non-Profits Running Campaigns<\/strong><\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"1524\" data-end=\"1679\">Non-profits often spend on awareness campaigns that bring users to landing pages for donations, sign-ups, or downloads\u2014but many users leave without acting.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"1681\" data-end=\"1947\"><strong data-start=\"1681\" data-end=\"1694\">Use case:<\/strong><br data-start=\"1694\" data-end=\"1697\" \/>An education-focused NGO runs a digital literacy campaign. Visitors read the impact stories but don\u2019t sign up or donate. A remarketing sequence can re-engage these users with a short video, a call to action, or success stories that reinforce urgency.<\/p>\n<h3 data-start=\"1949\" data-end=\"2009\">4. <strong data-start=\"1956\" data-end=\"2009\">SaaS and B2B Businesses With Long Decision Cycles<\/strong><\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"2011\" data-end=\"2261\">For software products, consulting firms, or B2B solutions, decisions are rarely made in one visit. Visitors explore, download a brochure, attend a webinar, and only then reach out. Remarketing is key to staying visible during that evaluation process.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"2263\" data-end=\"2494\"><strong data-start=\"2263\" data-end=\"2276\">Use case:<\/strong><br data-start=\"2276\" data-end=\"2279\" \/>A local CRM provider gets demo requests but loses leads before conversion. We run remarketing ads with pricing information, feature overviews, or customer success stories to nurture these leads back into the funnel.<\/p>\n<h3 data-start=\"2496\" data-end=\"2552\">5. <strong data-start=\"2503\" data-end=\"2552\">Any Business With Traffic But Low Conversions<\/strong><\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"2554\" data-end=\"2639\">Even if your business doesn&#8217;t fit neatly into one of the above categories, if you\u2019re:<\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"2640\" data-end=\"2794\">\n<li data-start=\"2640\" data-end=\"2685\">\n<p data-start=\"2642\" data-end=\"2685\">Getting traffic from social media or Google<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2686\" data-end=\"2737\">\n<p data-start=\"2688\" data-end=\"2737\">Not seeing proportional sales, sign-ups, or calls<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2738\" data-end=\"2794\">\n<p data-start=\"2740\" data-end=\"2794\">Not following up with that traffic in a structured way<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p data-start=\"2796\" data-end=\"2861\">\u2026then remarketing should be a core part of your digital strategy.<\/p>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column_inner][\/vc_row_inner][\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner][vc_column_text css=&#8221;&#8221;]<\/p>\n<h2 data-start=\"182\" data-end=\"217\">Requirements to Run Shopping Ads<\/h2>\n<p data-start=\"219\" data-end=\"498\">Before your products can appear in Google Shopping results, there are specific technical, compliance, and operational requirements you must meet. These are not optional; failure to meet them will result in product disapprovals, account suspension, or poor campaign performance.<\/p>\n<h3 data-start=\"500\" data-end=\"554\">1. An Active E-commerce Website with Product Pages<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"555\" data-end=\"694\">Google requires a functional, publicly accessible website that clearly lists the products you want to advertise.<br data-start=\"667\" data-end=\"670\" \/>Your site should have:<\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"695\" data-end=\"1112\">\n<li data-start=\"695\" data-end=\"758\">\n<p data-start=\"697\" data-end=\"758\"><strong data-start=\"697\" data-end=\"724\">Dedicated product pages<\/strong> with unique URLs for each item.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"759\" data-end=\"858\">\n<p data-start=\"761\" data-end=\"858\"><strong data-start=\"761\" data-end=\"794\">Detailed product descriptions<\/strong>, specifications, and clear pricing in Kenyan Shillings (KES).<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"859\" data-end=\"1025\">\n<p data-start=\"861\" data-end=\"1025\"><strong data-start=\"861\" data-end=\"892\">High-quality product images<\/strong> that load quickly and meet Google\u2019s image standards (minimum 100\u00d7100 pixels for non-apparel products, 250\u00d7250 pixels for apparel).<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"1026\" data-end=\"1112\">\n<p data-start=\"1028\" data-end=\"1112\"><strong data-start=\"1028\" data-end=\"1059\">Accurate stock availability<\/strong> so buyers do not click on items that are sold out.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p data-start=\"1114\" data-end=\"1265\">Google\u2019s automated crawlers will scan your website to confirm that the product data in your Merchant Center feed matches what is displayed on the site.<\/p>\n<h3 data-start=\"1267\" data-end=\"1313\">2. Verified Google Merchant Center Account<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"1314\" data-end=\"1424\">You must have a Google Merchant Center (GMC) account linked to your Google Ads account.<br data-start=\"1401\" data-end=\"1404\" \/>Key steps include:<\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"1425\" data-end=\"1878\">\n<li data-start=\"1425\" data-end=\"1525\">\n<p data-start=\"1427\" data-end=\"1525\"><strong data-start=\"1427\" data-end=\"1450\">Domain verification<\/strong> via HTML file upload, meta tag, Google Analytics, or Google Tag Manager.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"1526\" data-end=\"1609\">\n<p data-start=\"1528\" data-end=\"1609\"><strong data-start=\"1528\" data-end=\"1558\">Business information setup<\/strong> including store name, logo, and contact details.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"1610\" data-end=\"1721\">\n<p data-start=\"1612\" data-end=\"1721\"><strong data-start=\"1612\" data-end=\"1646\">Shipping and delivery settings<\/strong> configured for Kenyan locations and international markets if applicable.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"1722\" data-end=\"1878\">\n<p data-start=\"1724\" data-end=\"1878\"><strong data-start=\"1724\" data-end=\"1740\">Tax settings<\/strong> (while Kenya has no e-commerce-specific sales tax entry in Merchant Center, you must still ensure prices include VAT where applicable).<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p data-start=\"1880\" data-end=\"1960\">Without verification, your feed cannot be approved, and no Shopping Ads can run.<\/p>\n<h3 data-start=\"1962\" data-end=\"1991\">3. Compliant Product Feed<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"1992\" data-end=\"2140\">The product feed is the structured file (XML, CSV, or Google Sheets) that contains your product information.<br data-start=\"2100\" data-end=\"2103\" \/>To meet Google\u2019s feed requirements:<\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"2141\" data-end=\"2746\">\n<li data-start=\"2141\" data-end=\"2283\">\n<p data-start=\"2143\" data-end=\"2283\">Include <strong data-start=\"2151\" data-end=\"2179\">all mandatory attributes<\/strong> such as <code data-start=\"2188\" data-end=\"2192\">id<\/code>, <code data-start=\"2194\" data-end=\"2201\">title<\/code>, <code data-start=\"2203\" data-end=\"2216\">description<\/code>, <code data-start=\"2218\" data-end=\"2224\">link<\/code>, <code data-start=\"2226\" data-end=\"2238\">image_link<\/code>, <code data-start=\"2240\" data-end=\"2247\">price<\/code>, <code data-start=\"2249\" data-end=\"2263\">availability<\/code>, and <code data-start=\"2269\" data-end=\"2280\">condition<\/code>.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2284\" data-end=\"2396\">\n<p data-start=\"2286\" data-end=\"2396\">Add recommended attributes like GTIN (barcode number), MPN, and Google product category for better matching.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2397\" data-end=\"2500\">\n<p data-start=\"2399\" data-end=\"2500\">Use <strong data-start=\"2403\" data-end=\"2434\">clear and relevant keywords<\/strong> in product titles and descriptions to match buyer search terms.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2501\" data-end=\"2643\">\n<p data-start=\"2503\" data-end=\"2643\">Ensure that feed data matches your live website content exactly. Any price, availability, or currency mismatches can lead to disapprovals.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2644\" data-end=\"2746\">\n<p data-start=\"2646\" data-end=\"2746\">Remove prohibited items such as counterfeit goods, dangerous products, or restricted health items.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3 data-start=\"2748\" data-end=\"2800\">4. Approved Return, Refund, and Contact Policies<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"2801\" data-end=\"2877\">Google requires visible, accessible policies on your website that explain:<\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"2878\" data-end=\"3077\">\n<li data-start=\"2878\" data-end=\"2946\">\n<p data-start=\"2880\" data-end=\"2946\"><strong data-start=\"2880\" data-end=\"2917\">How customers can return products<\/strong> and within what timeframe.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2947\" data-end=\"3005\">\n<p data-start=\"2949\" data-end=\"3005\"><strong data-start=\"2949\" data-end=\"2975\">Conditions for refunds<\/strong> and how they are processed.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"3006\" data-end=\"3077\">\n<p data-start=\"3008\" data-end=\"3077\"><strong data-start=\"3008\" data-end=\"3027\">Contact options<\/strong> such as a phone number, email, or contact form.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p data-start=\"3079\" data-end=\"3143\">These pages build trust and are mandatory for policy compliance.<\/p>\n<h3 data-start=\"3145\" data-end=\"3177\">5. Linked Google Ads Account<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"3178\" data-end=\"3478\">Your Merchant Center account must be linked to your Google Ads account to run campaigns. This connection allows you to create Shopping campaigns using the products in your feed.<br data-start=\"3355\" data-end=\"3358\" \/>Once linked, you can segment products, set bids, apply targeting, and measure performance from the Google Ads interface.<\/p>\n<h3 data-start=\"3480\" data-end=\"3508\">6. Operational Readiness<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"3509\" data-end=\"3585\">Even with a fully compliant setup, success depends on operational factors:<\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"3586\" data-end=\"3789\">\n<li data-start=\"3586\" data-end=\"3642\">\n<p data-start=\"3588\" data-end=\"3642\"><strong data-start=\"3588\" data-end=\"3611\">Reliable fulfilment<\/strong> to ensure timely deliveries.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"3643\" data-end=\"3701\">\n<p data-start=\"3645\" data-end=\"3701\"><strong data-start=\"3645\" data-end=\"3675\">Accurate inventory updates<\/strong> to prevent overselling.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"3702\" data-end=\"3789\">\n<p data-start=\"3704\" data-end=\"3789\"><strong data-start=\"3704\" data-end=\"3737\">Customer service availability<\/strong> to respond to pre- and post-sale queries quickly.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p data-start=\"3791\" data-end=\"3896\">A technically correct campaign can still underperform if the customer experience is poor after the click.<\/p>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column_inner][\/vc_row_inner][\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row bg_type=&#8221;bg_color&#8221;][vc_column][vc_cta h2=&#8221;Showcase your products where buyers are already searching.&#8221; h2_font_container=&#8221;tag:h2|text_align:left|color:%23000000&#8243; h2_use_theme_fonts=&#8221;yes&#8221; h2_css_animation=&#8221;fadeInLeft&#8221; h4_font_container=&#8221;tag:h4|text_align:left|color:%230A0A0A&#8221; h4_use_theme_fonts=&#8221;yes&#8221; shape=&#8221;square&#8221; style=&#8221;flat&#8221; color=&#8221;grey&#8221; add_button=&#8221;right&#8221; btn_title=&#8221;Contact Us&#8221; btn_shape=&#8221;square&#8221; btn_color=&#8221;warning&#8221; btn_i_align=&#8221;right&#8221; btn_i_icon_fontawesome=&#8221;fa fa-solid fa-paper-plane&#8221; btn_css_animation=&#8221;bounceIn&#8221; css=&#8221;&#8221; use_custom_fonts_h2=&#8221;true&#8221; use_custom_fonts_h4=&#8221;true&#8221; btn_add_icon=&#8221;true&#8221; btn_link=&#8221;url:%23!%2Fcontact&#8221;]Contact Aminifu Digital Agency today.[\/vc_cta][\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner][vc_column_text css=&#8221;&#8221;]<\/p>\n<h2 data-start=\"179\" data-end=\"228\">Why Choose Aminifu Digital Agency for Shopping Ads<\/h2>\n<p data-start=\"230\" data-end=\"572\">Running Google Shopping Ads effectively requires more than simply uploading a product feed and setting a budget. It demands a combination of technical expertise, market knowledge, and continuous optimisation to achieve profitable results. Aminifu Digital Agency delivers all three, backed by a proven track record in the Kenyan e-commerce market.<\/p>\n<h3 data-start=\"574\" data-end=\"615\">Proven E-commerce Ad Results in Kenya<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"616\" data-end=\"1127\">We have successfully managed Shopping Ads campaigns for Kenyan retailers in sectors such as electronics, fashion, beauty, homeware, and niche consumer goods. Our campaigns have consistently delivered measurable improvements in sales volume, conversion rates, and return on ad spend (ROAS). For example, a Kenyan electronics store increased sales by 85% within three months of our Shopping Ads launch, while a fashion retailer achieved a nine-times ROAS through precise product segmentation and bid optimisation.<\/p>\n<h3 data-start=\"1129\" data-end=\"1165\">Google-Certified Ads Specialists<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"1166\" data-end=\"1505\">Our team holds official Google Ads certifications, including Shopping Ads specialisations. This ensures that every campaign is built to Google\u2019s best practices, from feed compliance to campaign structure. Certification also gives us access to beta features and early updates, allowing us to test new tools before they are widely available.<\/p>\n<h3 data-start=\"1507\" data-end=\"1550\">Deep Knowledge of Local Buyer Behaviour<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"1551\" data-end=\"1975\">Kenya\u2019s e-commerce landscape is different from markets in Europe or North America. Purchase patterns are shaped by factors such as mobile-first browsing, regional price sensitivity, seasonal spikes (e.g., back-to-school, festive seasons), and preferred delivery options. We build campaigns that take these nuances into account, ensuring ads are not only technically correct but also contextually relevant to Kenyan shoppers.<\/p>\n<h3 data-start=\"1977\" data-end=\"2004\">Full-Service Management<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"2005\" data-end=\"2074\">We offer a complete end-to-end Shopping Ads service. This includes:<\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"2075\" data-end=\"2446\">\n<li data-start=\"2075\" data-end=\"2128\">\n<p data-start=\"2077\" data-end=\"2128\"><strong data-start=\"2077\" data-end=\"2126\">Google Merchant Center setup and verification<\/strong><\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2129\" data-end=\"2203\">\n<p data-start=\"2131\" data-end=\"2203\"><strong data-start=\"2131\" data-end=\"2173\">Product feed creation and optimisation<\/strong> for higher impression share<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2204\" data-end=\"2287\">\n<p data-start=\"2206\" data-end=\"2287\"><strong data-start=\"2206\" data-end=\"2224\">Campaign setup<\/strong> using the most effective structure for your budget and goals<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2288\" data-end=\"2363\">\n<p data-start=\"2290\" data-end=\"2363\"><strong data-start=\"2290\" data-end=\"2328\">Performance tracking and analytics<\/strong> with clear, accessible reporting<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2364\" data-end=\"2446\">\n<p data-start=\"2366\" data-end=\"2446\"><strong data-start=\"2366\" data-end=\"2390\">Ongoing optimisation<\/strong> to keep ads competitive in changing market conditions<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p data-start=\"2448\" data-end=\"2552\">This eliminates the need to work with multiple providers for different parts of your Shopping Ads setup.<\/p>\n<h3 data-start=\"2554\" data-end=\"2598\">Transparent Reporting and Measurable ROI<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"2599\" data-end=\"3018\">We provide clear monthly reports that show exactly how your budget has been spent, the performance of each product category, and the resulting sales. Using metrics like CTR, CPC, ROAS, and impression share, we break down what is working, where adjustments are needed, and how your campaigns are progressing against agreed targets. This transparency ensures you can link your ad spend directly to your sales performance.<\/p>\n<h3 data-start=\"3020\" data-end=\"3061\">Competitive Edge Over Larger Agencies<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"3062\" data-end=\"3349\">While larger agencies may focus on high-budget corporate clients, we provide the same level of technical expertise while remaining agile and responsive. Our focus is on delivering profitable campaigns for each client, regardless of size, with rapid adjustments based on performance data.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"3351\" data-end=\"3680\">Choosing Aminifu Digital Agency means working with a partner who understands both the technical side of Google Shopping Ads and the realities of selling online in Kenya. Our combination of expertise, market insight, and transparent processes positions us as the ideal choice for e-commerce brands that want to scale sales profitably.<\/p>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column_inner][\/vc_row_inner][\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row bg_type=&#8221;bg_color&#8221;][vc_column][vc_cta h2=&#8221;artner with Aminifu Digital Agency and turn Google Shopping into a consistent sales driver.&#8221; h2_font_container=&#8221;tag:h2|text_align:left|color:%23000000&#8243; h2_use_theme_fonts=&#8221;yes&#8221; h2_css_animation=&#8221;fadeInLeft&#8221; h4_font_container=&#8221;tag:h4|text_align:left|color:%230A0A0A&#8221; h4_use_theme_fonts=&#8221;yes&#8221; shape=&#8221;square&#8221; style=&#8221;flat&#8221; color=&#8221;grey&#8221; add_button=&#8221;right&#8221; btn_title=&#8221;Contact Us&#8221; btn_shape=&#8221;square&#8221; btn_color=&#8221;warning&#8221; btn_i_align=&#8221;right&#8221; btn_i_icon_fontawesome=&#8221;fa fa-solid fa-paper-plane&#8221; btn_css_animat