053\" data-end=\"1120\">Implemented GA4 tracking for ROAS and category-level performance.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p data-start=\"1122\" data-end=\"1374\"><strong data-start=\"1122\" data-end=\"1132\">After:<\/strong><br data-start=\"1132\" data-end=\"1135\" \/>Within 90 days, sales volume increased by 85%, and cost per acquisition (CPA) dropped by 32%. Their Shopping Ads now hold an average impression share of 74% for core product categories, consistently appearing in the top carousel positions.<\/p>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column_inner][\/vc_row_inner][\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row full_width=&#8221;stretch_row&#8221; bg_type=&#8221;bg_color&#8221; css=&#8221;.vc_custom_1717845133697{padding-top: 30px !important;padding-bottom: 30px !important;}&#8221; bg_color_value=&#8221;#f4f4f4&#8243; el_id=&#8221;!\/contact&#8221;][vc_column]<div id=\"ultimate-heading-1619695ec19457cfc\" class=\"uvc-heading ult-adjust-bottom-margin ultimate-heading-1619695ec19457cfc uvc-2786  uvc-heading-default-font-sizes\" data-hspacer=\"line_with_icon\" data-hline_width=\"100\" data-hicon_type=\"selector\" data-hborder_style=\"solid\" data-hborder_height=\"5\" data-hborder_color=\"#3697ca\" data-icon_width=\"32\" data-hfixer=\"5\"  data-halign=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center\"><div class=\"uvc-main-heading ult-responsive\"  data-ultimate-target='.uvc-heading.ultimate-heading-1619695ec19457cfc h2'  data-responsive-json-new='{\"font-size\":\"\",\"line-height\":\"\"}' ><h2 style=\"--font-weight:theme;\">Get in touch and let's discuss your Digital Marketing needs<\/h2><\/div><div class=\"uvc-heading-spacer line_with_icon\" style=\"topheight:32px;\"><div class=\"ult-just-icon-wrapper  \"><div class=\"align-icon\" style=\"text-align:center;\">\n<div class=\"aio-icon none \"  style=\"color:#3697ca;font-size:32px;display:inline-block;\">\n\t<i class=\"fas fa-angle-down\"><\/i>\n<\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><div class=\"uvc-sub-heading ult-responsive\"  data-ultimate-target='.uvc-heading.ulti